data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Stonecrest, South Fork! This remarkable 2-year-old residence offers extraordinary features. The continuous ceramic tile flooring graces the living areas, creating a seamless flow.    The open-concept design effortlessly blends relaxation and entertainment. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and modern cabinetry. Meal prep becomes a delight as you engage with loved ones in the adjoining living area.    Convenience is paramount with proximity to shopping, dining, nature parks, hospitals, the VA clinic, and major roadways. Easy access to I-75 and US-301 connects you to Tampa's city life or Sarasota's beaches.    Experience comfort, luxury, and convenience. Schedule a viewing today and step into a life where every day feels like a dream come true. This is your perfect home!
